38#include <config.h>
39#include "ntp_types.h"
40#include "trimble.h"
41
42cmd_info_t *
43trimble_convert(
44 unsigned int cmd,
45 cmd_info_t *tbl
46 )
47{
48 int i;
49
50 for (i = 0; tbl[i].cmd != 0xFF; i++)
51 {
52 if (tbl[i].cmd == cmd)
53 return &tbl[i];
54 }
55 return 0;
56}
